videos.description: Indiana's Romeo Langford draws a double-team, but loops a bounce pass around traffic to Juwan Morgan for the and-1 finish.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Langford skips nifty pass for Morgan and-1) 2019/3/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Langford skips nifty pass for Morgan and-1

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods of Ohio State sizes up Evan Fitzner and buries the mid-range jumper to force an Indiana timeout.
